# Portfolio listing automation

https://ymd-portfolio-site.pages.dev/ is the **personal portfolio** for **Web apps that do not need store review**.

Store legal pages live on **personal-site** (separate).

## Agent must

- When a Web app gets a public URL, run **yourself**:
  `node scripts/publish-app-listing.mjs --name "..." --url "https://..."`
  (registers, commits, pushes, triggers Cloudflare Pages). Never ask the user to run it.
- Embed privacy/terms/support links in the app footer (see `docs/WEB_PUBLISH.md` / `legal/embed-snippet.html`).
- Prefer setting the GitHub repo **Website** field so daily `sync-apps` keeps picking it up.
- Confirm live list at https://ymd-portfolio-site.pages.dev/ after deploy.

## CI already does

- On push / daily cron: `npm run build` (`sync-apps.mjs`) then Cloudflare Pages deploy.
- Preview / legal-hub noise URLs are excluded via `config/apps.config.json`.

## Do not

- Tell the user to run `npm run register-app` / `sync:apps`.
- Treat portfolio listings as optional follow-ups for the user.
